      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1771728450373,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "functional req: \n- view single / list of problems \n- solve the problem: write the code  +  add testcases + execute  \n- view past submissions (user specific)\n\n(out of scope)\n- view discussions : view / create / comment / edit   \n- leaderborad\n\nnon-func: \n- CAP : focus on availability; we want to be showing / executing current code for the user \n- low latency : should not take forever to execute \n- isolation: run only user specific code (in their specific language)\n- scalability ; many 10k people could be using this at once  \n\noutofscope: \n- redundandcy / fault tolerant \n",
      "fontSize": 20.076042811086236,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "functional req: \n- view single / list of problems \n- solve the problem: write the code  +  add testcases + execute  \n- view past submissions (user specific)\n\n(out of scope)\n- view discussions : view / create / comment / edit   \n- leaderborad\n\nnon-func: \n- CAP : focus on availability; we want to be showing / executing current code for the user \n- low latency : should not take forever to execute \n- isolation: run only user specific code (in their specific language)\n- scalability ; many 10k people could be using this at once  \n\noutofscope: \n- redundandcy / fault tolerant \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
